# Zurvan Linux — §3 KDE Plasma 6.7 Desktop Environment
# (package-manifest.md §3, with Debian 13 / Plasma 6 substitutions)
#
# NOTE on substitutions vs. the original manifest:
#  - `plasma-workspace-wayland` does NOT exist in Debian 13: the Wayland session
#    is part of `plasma-workspace` itself in Plasma 6. Verified via madison.
#  - `khotkeys` was REMOVED in Plasma 6 (custom shortcuts moved into KDE's
#    built-in global-accel system). Omitted to avoid a missing-package build
#    failure.
plasma-desktop
plasma-workspace
plasma-nm
plasma-pa
kscreen
powerdevil
kde-style-breeze
